    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>
                        <persName><name ref="Gausbertus">Gospertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">mulinario</rs>, avitator infra <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs> ista <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Queen"
                            >Lucense</placeName> prope <geogName ref="#estates/3304"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Mention #Queen"><rs key="#Curtes"
                                >curte</rs> domne <rs key="#Queen">regine</rs></geogName>, filius
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Lazarus">Lazari</name></persName> viene
                        posto da <persName ref="#people/3305" key="#Bishops">Hieremias</persName>
                        gratia Dei <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> (…) livellario ordine (…) in
                        casa illa, in qua ego ipsi abitare videor prope suprascripta <geogName
                            ref="#estates/3304" key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Mention #Queen"><rs
                                key="#Curtes">curte</rs> domne <rs key="#Queen"
                            >regine</rs></geogName>, pertinentes <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        vestre <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1705" key="#Churches">Sancti Petri
                            que dicitur ad Vincula, et Sancti Geminiani</orgName>; iam dicta casa
                        cum orto, <rs key="#Processing_units">sive riparia et sepe mulinaria</rs>,
                        ubi ego ipsi modo <rs key="#Mills">molino</rs>, avere visu sum, (…). Obbligo
                        di in ipsa casa residere et abitare (…); et tam ipsa casa quam et orto (…)
                        bene excolere et gubernare seo meliorare (…). Censo (pro iustitia): per
                        singulos annos in festivitate suprascripte ecclesie Sancti Geminiani in
                        suprascripta ecclesia ad presbitero illo qui pro tempore in ipsa ecclesia
                        ordinatus fuerit, census reddere debeamus argentum denarios bonos
                        expendiviles numero tres tantum; et pro suprascripta riparia, dum predicto
                            <rs key="#Mills">molino</rs> inibi abuerimus (…) ad parte prefate
                        ecclesie Sancti Geminiani vel suis rectoribus, per singulos annos per omnem
                        ebdomadas, uno sistario de <rs key="#Cereals">grano mundo</rs> ad legitimo
                        sistario mensurato; et a mandato vestro venire (…) legem et iustitiam
                        faciendum (…). Pena: argentum solidos quinquaginta (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Adalfredus"
                            >Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                            >Adalpertus</name></persName> filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Baldipertus">Baldiperti</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Hildiprandus</name></persName> filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Ildefredus">Hiltifridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Philippus/de Suborbano">Filippi</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/487">Suborbano</placeName></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Teofridus"
                            >Teufridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scabinus</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
